      {
        "text": "不",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000004",
    "sentence": "是宜傳。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000005",
    "sentence": "羅衣輕，不知其鄉里。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000006",
    "sentence": "滑稽通變，一時諧謔，多所規諷。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000007",
    "sentence": "興宗敗於李元昊也，單騎突出，幾不得脫。",
