        "text": "李元昊",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000008",
    "sentence": "先是，元昊獲遼人，輒劓其鼻，有奔北者惟恐追及。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "元昊",
        "label": "PER"
      },
      {
        "text": "遼",
        "label": "ORG"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000009",
    "sentence": "故羅衣輕止之曰：「且觀鼻在否？」",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "羅衣輕",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000010",
    "sentence": "上怒，以毳索系帳後，將殺之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000011",
    "sentence": "太子笑曰：「打諢底不是黃幡綽！」",
