      {
        "text": "太子",
        "label": "TITLE"
      },
      {
        "text": "黃幡綽",
        "label": "PER"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000012",
    "sentence": "羅衣輕應聲曰：「行兵底亦不是唐太宗！」",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "羅衣輕",
        "label": "PER"
      },
      {
        "text": "唐太宗",
        "label": "TITLE"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000013",
    "sentence": "上聞而釋之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_010_109_000014",
    "sentence": "上嘗與太弟重元狎昵，宴酣，許以千秋萬歲後傳位。",
